Title: Alden Power Reclining Living Room Set
Body HTML:
Relax in style with the Alden Power Collection.  Featuring supple gray leather seating, contrast accent stitching, and contemporary style that makes this collection look as good as it feels. The set includes Reclining Sofa, Reclining Console Loveseat, and Reclining Chair

 

DIMENSIONS

Sofa- 90" W x 40" D x 40" H

Loveseat - 81" W x 40" D x 40" H

Recliner - 39" W x 40" D x 41" H
